{"tid":1123392,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[壞撚左GTX 970]  好奇想知壞咩，之後換咩卡好？","createTime":"2019-04-24T12:16:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T11:02:53.000Z","uid":231905,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0065a852fea497624caffae9fcb9714f4a717e16","tid":1123392,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T12:16:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SQ4BBYD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSQ4BBYD.jpg&h=aaaaf598&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n是咁的，上圖 Zotac 970 4GB買左3年<br />\n3個月前試過開機冇output，拎左去保養，保撚左一個月整返<br />\n今日開機就唔得了 (試過換舊display，100% work，所以肯定係gpu出事，其他spec無謂貼了)<br />\n1. 開機<br />\n2. 其他所有fan轉+display fan轉<br />\n3. mouse keyboard 著燈<br />\n4. 過三四秒，display fan就會冇力停左 + mouse keyboard熄燈<br />\n5. display fan轉 + mouse keyboard 著燈<br />\n6. 無限loop<br />\n7. monitor一直no signal<br />\n本身覺得係output問題，但見佢搞到mouse同keyboard都會不停boot，display風扇又係boot boot下咁，覺得好奇怪，想睇下咁多位大佬有咩意見。<br />\n<br />\n另外睇過gtx 1660 玩apex等等1080p 高效都可以60fps，夠我用了。<br />\n1660依家入手可以捱到幾多年1080p 60fps?<br />\n如果有跟開Total war three kingdoms 巴打，1660夠唔夠打？<br />\n定係會推薦買貴左2060？"},{"pid":"d119432b8e6b60b686e352aa661d4845f337e08d","tid":1123392,"uid":2471,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T12:28:32.000Z","msg":"添少少上2080ti 夠用幾年"},{"pid":"a0066932ac15fff861a074fe578b29499badc2a5","tid":1123392,"uid":138724,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T12:32:49.000Z","msg":"你970換1660個差別唔會好大<br />\n<br />\n你想玩3年以上建議2060會穩陣d<br />\n<br />\n畫質又可以開高d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw張卡連死兩次會唔會關隻火牛事？<br />\n巴打用緊咩火牛"},{"pid":"e4959cf598a167c0a84f86812059fa800549f5b3","tid":1123392,"uid":235152,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T12:36:15.000Z","msg":"2060勁過1070接近1070Ti<br />\n2K以上畫質有Dgame效能同1070Ti平手<br />\n1660勁1060好似50%到<br />\n<br />\n只係貴一千首選2060"},{"pid":"2ef345ec3319bcee5d45ddda20801cfe7